data.description: Welcome to your dream abode in the prestigious Parkridge community! This exceptional 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home is a gem featuring vaulted ceilings and natural light cascading throughout. The interior features laminate and tile flooring throughout. The bright kitchen showcases tons of cabinet space and a breakfast bar. The spacious floorplan has sizable bedrooms with ample closet space. Step outside onto your covered patio and tranquil surroundings. With its seamless fusion of modern design, natural illumination, and covered outdoor oasis, this home in Parkridge is not just a dwelling but a canvas for a life well-lived. Experience the pinnacle of elegance and comfort in this desirable community!
